<section class="library__chapter">
	<h2 class="library__chapter-title">Messaging</h2>
	<p class="library__chapter-purpose">When communicating with our customers and suppliers, it's important to consider the context. It's important we keep a consistent, yet considerate voice and tone throughout our brand. Below are examples for a guide in how we strive to do just that.</p>
	<article class="library__persona">
		<h3 class="library__persona-title">Facility Engineer</h3>
		<img src="http://cdn2.dropmark.com/72454/c77c31b8469d7d1fe92583e142963ba594918bad/facility-engineer.jpg" />
		<section class="library__persona-attributes">
			<h4 class="is-alias">Also Reffered To As:</h4>
			<p>Building Engineer</p>
			<h4 class="is-goals">UX Goals:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Be Helpful</li>
				<li>Be Responsive (in Feedback)</li>
				<li>Be Assistive</li>
				<li>Be Handy</li>
				<li>Be Factual</li>
			</ul>
			<h4 class="is-traits">Behaviors/Traits:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Initiates work requests</li>
				<li>View equipment (&amp; history by facility)</li>
				<li>Receives Notifications (Need to change filters, perform inspection, etc)</li>
				<li>Orders Parts</li>
				<li>Reviews scope RFQ's and pricing</li>
				<li>Likes to be collaborative with Field Tech's</li>
				<li>Desk typically in a dark corner in buried part of building (think janitor's office)</li>
				<li>Walkie Talkie </li>
				<li>Has both Preferred Vendors (Invites them as well) &amp;</li>
				<li>One of few mobile viewers. Needs to do everything on fly.</li>
			</ul>
			<h4 class="is-influence">Influencers:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Pressures from Property Manager and hierarchy</li>
				<li>Speed (e.g. Do they have feedback on *when* a vendor will be on-site?)</li>
				<li>Feedback loops, being informed (urgency could cause work outside Ravti)</li>
				<li>Mechanical contractor perks (baseball games, trips to the keys, etc.)</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</article>
	<article class="library__persona">
		<h3 class="library__persona-title">Property Manager</h3>
		<img src="http://cdn2.dropmark.com/72454/0e720e36bde23744f97c611a6d0ccc505eef41f4/property-manager.jpg" />
		<section class="library__persona-attributes">
			<h4 class="is-alias">Also Reffered To As:</h4>
			<p>P.M. , Manager</p>
			<h4 class="is-goals">UX Goals:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Be an organizer</li>
				<li>Be resourceful</li>
				<li>Be insightful</li>
				<li>Be holistic</li>
				<li>Be obvious</li>
			</ul>
			<h4 class="is-traits">Behaviors/Traits:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Makes final call on which proposal to go with</li>
				<li>Biggest pain in a** of her day: (getting more than 1 price)</li>
				<li>She wants to see high level: how much $ we spending on HVAC (all of building budget)</li>
				<li>Leasing (new tenant wants to know life expectancy on equipment, what the condition and diagnostics for new space is going to look like: give new onboardings a exported set )</li>
				<li>Leasing compliance</li>
				<li>Initiate maintenance programs</li>
				<li>Wants high level summaries of services being done (has to be kept in loop)</li>
				<li>FYI: 80/20 Female to Male role ratio</li>
			</ul>
			<h4 class="is-influence">Influencers:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Budget (Typically agreed on w/ management for Quaterly / Annual Forecasting)</li>
				<li>Time. Think busy and impatient</li>
				<li>Org hierarchy. Has upper management to please</li>
				<li>Doesn't enjoy not being a domain expert. Wants to "speak the language"</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</article>
	<article class="library__persona">
		<h3 class="library__persona-title">Field Technician</h3>
		<img src="http://cdn2.dropmark.com/72454/9ac5a131ae4ae1a672605de61da6875968bf07a7/field-tech.jpg" />
		<section class="library__persona-attributes">
			<h4 class="is-alias">Also Reffered To As:</h4>
			<p>Mechanical, Mechancial Contractor, Tech, Vendor</p>
			<h4 class="is-goals">UX Goals:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Be obvious</li>
				<li>Be easy</li>
				<li>Be un-intrusive</li>
				<li>Be lightweight</li>
				<li>Be effortless</li>
				<li>Be convenient</li>
			</ul>
			<h4 class="is-traits">Behaviors/Traits:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>We're cutting into his pie</li>
				<li>Has processes already has to abide with, we're a thorn</li>
				<li>Dirt under the fingernails type person</li>
				<li>Dishevled, does work, passes tickets/reports to teamember back @ office</li>
				<li>On the fly</li>
			</ul>
			<h4 class="is-influence">Influencers:</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>Weather (Summer Heat + Rooftops)</li>
				<li>Time (Everytime come out, automatic trip-charge plus hourly rate</li>
				<li>A limited resource, service call comes up, will leave preventative maintenance</li>
				<li>Day to day wear and tear (greasy hands, cracked mobile screen, etc.)</li>
				<li>Stubborness to old ways</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</article>
</section>